Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.19,0:23:26.28,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}耀眼的Butterfly
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.28,0:23:29.53,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}這一切——
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.53,0:23:33.71,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}現在都將改寫
