Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:02.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凶真
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.32,0:00:05.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.14,0:00:06.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能成為
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.14,0:00:09.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救世主
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.21,0:05:50.66,mail,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閃光的指壓師\N拜託你\N我也想發D-Mail！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.62,0:05:57.84,mail,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行嗎？\N可以的吧？\N拜託！\N萌郁
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.22,0:06:04.55,mail,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是\N實驗室成員中的一員吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.52,0:12:39.90,up,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}（希望你能成為救世主）
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.85,0:00:19.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然讓我…成為救世主？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.86,0:00:21.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無聊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.08,0:00:23.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是一個瘋狂的科學家
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.44,0:00:26.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,企盼的只是破壞和混沌…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.35,0:00:34.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.94,0:00:44.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從現在起  掌管過去的女神作戰重新啟動
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.29,0:00:47.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布朗氏還在樓下啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.29,0:00:47.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.04,0:00:48.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.84,0:00:51.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說了的  我反對
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.79,0:00:55.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊  白天不是挺合作的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.51,0:00:56.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白天？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.21,0:00:59.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼你果然…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.28,0:01:03.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  實驗已經進行了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.58,0:01:06.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經用D-Mail改變了過去了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.03,0:01:07.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的假的…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.03,0:01:10.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是說世界線已經變了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.24,0:01:11.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕是的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.40,0:01:16.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此你們喪失了一部分改變之前的記憶
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.19,0:01:19.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是關於六合彩什麼的那件事嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.57,0:01:20.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.62,0:01:25.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  為什麼只有你一個人還保存著記憶啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.39,0:01:30.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提托說了  我有著某種力量
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.90,0:01:35.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了證實這個  也有必要再一次移動世界線
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.65,0:01:37.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,力量？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.30,0:01:41.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算穿越了世界線  也能夠保有記憶的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.32,0:01:44.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(340,325)\fscy80\fscx80}reading  steiner
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.32,0:01:44.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魔眼「命運探知」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.85,0:03:41.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿至
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.43,0:03:44.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無發信記錄  收信…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.67,0:03:47.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  D-Mail發到5天前了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.66,0:03:48.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.01,0:03:50.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過去…改變了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.37,0:03:53.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼你會記著這事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.35,0:04:01.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給5天前的阿至發送D-Mail
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.54,0:04:04.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告訴他菲伊莉斯杯上的牌面佈置
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.38,0:04:07.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後阿至應該就能贏
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.12,0:04:10.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊真由氏？  我有件事想問一下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.85,0:04:13.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前的菲伊莉斯杯上我…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.48,0:04:16.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,輸了  被秒殺？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.94,0:04:18.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.41,0:04:19.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝  再見
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.63,0:04:28.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發給阿至的簡訊並沒有改變過去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.95,0:04:31.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遊戲的流程應該改變了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.94,0:04:36.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說就那種程度世界線是不會變動的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.70,0:04:41.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用更明瞭的方式改變過去就不行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.39,0:04:43.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.27,0:04:47.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我並不是贊成進行實驗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.00,0:04:50.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  你怎麼想
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.40,0:04:54.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對於只有你留有記憶這種事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.35,0:04:58.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說了  這是魔眼「命運探知」的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.39,0:05:05.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了證實這一點  下面就輪到你發D-Mail了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.74,0:05:08.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不要
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.47,0:05:11.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你擔心發生時間悖論嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.55,0:05:16.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,改變過去什麼的  總覺得有點卑鄙的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.11,0:05:23.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的人生雖然只有18年  但是我並不想改變
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.78,0:05:27.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,包括失敗  那也是我的人生
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.27,0:05:31.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是你卻最喜歡做實驗  不是嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.67,0:05:33.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜…喜歡有錯嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.30,0:05:38.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說你只想袖手旁觀  然後笑看他人犧牲
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.52,0:05:40.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  真是一個瘋狂科學家
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.18,0:05:41.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.94,0:05:44.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  說真的…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.28,0:05:54.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說真的  要想改良D-Mail…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.60,0:06:01.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然除了繼續進行試驗之外…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.97,0:06:03.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萌郁小姐嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.27,0:06:05.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真煩
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.24,0:06:06.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.37,0:06:18.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果還是由著她來了…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.29,0:06:25.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  到家了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.93,0:06:27.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可麗餅真好吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.10,0:00:01.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.14,0:06:31.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼  看上去很閒嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.04,0:06:33.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在等人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.78,0:06:37.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  不准嚇唬綯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.08,0:06:39.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我什麼也沒做啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.67,0:06:40.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧  綯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.83,0:06:44.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用理這種傢伙快走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.71,0:06:46.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.99,0:06:49.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真由理姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.85,0:06:51.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘟嘟嚕
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.78,0:06:54.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給你這個
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.11,0:06:56.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.71,0:07:00.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給  小岡倫也有
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.28,0:07:08.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.69,0:07:10.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好  鈴姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.45,0:07:11.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打工的姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.48,0:07:16.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂  那之後怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.66,0:07:17.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼怎麼樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.45,0:07:18.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時間機器啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.04,0:07:20.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你問了約翰·提托了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.00,0:07:25.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  但是那傢伙說的是否正確我還不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.53,0:07:28.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？  哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.57,0:07:31.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼你這麼較真
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.33,0:07:34.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是一個提托宅對吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.46,0:07:36.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.72,0:07:39.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是紅莉栖  嘟嘟嚕
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.37,0:07:40.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.06,0:07:55.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  又火星四濺了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.38,0:07:56.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她怎麼回事啊  真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.65,0:07:59.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵架不好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.57,0:08:02.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要擔心  沒關係的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.61,0:08:04.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.97,0:08:06.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,禁止發私人信件
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.57,0:08:08.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最好是可以明白確認過去是否改變
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.07,0:08:10.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,簡單的內容
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.35,0:08:18.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「四天前我換了手機」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.70,0:08:22.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「但是想告訴自己不要換比較好」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.24,0:08:23.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.84,0:08:26.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是過去改變了的話桐生小姐的手機就會改變
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.56,0:08:28.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一目瞭然
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.23,0:08:31.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  開始實驗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.13,0:08:45.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  電話微波爐（暫定）啟動
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.72,0:08:50.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圓圓的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.88,0:08:51.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.93,0:08:57.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,岡部…因為弄錯了凶真師傅告訴我的六合彩號碼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.47,0:08:58.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以這是賠禮
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.14,0:09:00.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦…  是  是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.40,0:09:05.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…  嗯  心意很好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.34,0:09:08.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的心眼睜開的日子應該不遠了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.16,0:09:10.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  那麼我就告辭了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.02,0:09:12.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就要走了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.31,0:09:15.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看上去你們正在忙著呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.67,0:09:17.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告辭了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.13,0:09:22.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次就來穿穿真由氏的COS吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.27,0:09:23.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對…對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.50,0:09:25.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我對那個還是有點…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.31,0:09:26.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是不行嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.80,0:09:29.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我倒覺得很適合你的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.69,0:09:30.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  下次見
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.74,0:09:32.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.88,0:09:36.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是個好孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.20,0:09:38.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.90,0:10:04.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是…這種感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.65,0:10:06.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.95,0:10:10.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過去…改變了？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.08,0:10:23.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閃…閃光的指壓師在哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.27,0:10:25.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閃？  啥？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.30,0:10:27.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用日語就OK
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.39,0:10:41.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琉佳子…沒來過嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.26,0:10:44.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琉佳？  嗯  沒來過啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.23,0:10:47.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼萌郁呢？  萌郁去哪了？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.42,0:10:49.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萌郁？  是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.18,0:10:53.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桐生萌郁  今天沒來這裡嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.61,0:10:55.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.60,0:10:57.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是誰啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.43,0:11:04.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桐生萌郁？  我也沒聽說過
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.31,0:11:04.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.35,0:11:08.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說  你又發了D-Mail？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.20,0:11:10.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等  怎麼回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.09,0:11:16.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過去改變了  萌郁這個人的存在本身就消失了？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.99,0:11:17.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.08,0:11:23.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收信記錄還留有萌郁到7月31日為止的簡訊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.65,0:11:35.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「怎麼了？」
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.85,0:11:37.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「對不起  現在有些忙」
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.81,0:11:39.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「過會再發簡訊」
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.96,0:11:45.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說四天之前
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.47,0:11:48.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收到簡訊的桐生…萌郁
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.24,0:11:51.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她的行動發生了改變
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.27,0:11:52.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於是就沒來實驗室
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.16,0:11:55.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣子過去就改變了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.54,0:11:57.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.46,0:12:02.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且  這回也是只有你才記得
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.63,0:12:05.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  Reading  Steiner什麼的？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.29,0:12:08.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,順便說下這個造語太丟人了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.84,0:12:10.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得還是別用為好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.85,0:12:14.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不需要你個人的見解
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.65,0:12:18.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,越過世界線仍維持記憶的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.47,0:12:21.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.19,0:12:25.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.97,0:12:29.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話到明天再說
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.93,0:12:32.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小岡倫  明天見
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.57,0:12:36.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個力量是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.75,0:12:41.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  我…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.72,0:12:46.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的那幫傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.12,0:12:49.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真能睡在實驗室裡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.62,0:12:52.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說那就是瘋狂科學家
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.62,0:12:56.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了  下次大家一起開留宿會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.27,0:12:57.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了男人們呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.40,0:13:01.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了  要不要來我住的賓館
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.13,0:13:02.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.39,0:13:03.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.49,0:13:06.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  那下次就去打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.84,0:13:13.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琉佳  嘟嘟嚕
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.94,0:13:18.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.10,0:13:21.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.78,0:13:24.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然沒帶妖刀五月雨來？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.65,0:13:25.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.08,0:13:26.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行哦小岡倫
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.84,0:13:30.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琉佳今天是真由氏的客人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.59,0:13:33.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是來穿真由氏做的COS的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.59,0:13:34.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我  我…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.70,0:13:37.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來來  琉佳  變身吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.14,0:13:39.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,變身變身
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.34,0:13:40.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所  所以說我…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.55,0:13:43.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧  脫衣服脫衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.49,0:13:46.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要摸那種地方
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.73,0:13:49.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了  我自己穿
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.14,0:13:50.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以去那邊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.01,0:13:53.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿這個是有訣竅的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.60,0:13:56.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了不要脫
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.48,0:13:58.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常…百合
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.21,0:13:59.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.38,0:14:01.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琉佳子是男的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.40,0:14:03.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.50,0:14:05.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就更不知廉恥了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.94,0:14:15.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是雷Net的小閃
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.12,0:14:20.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不出所料非常可愛喲  琉佳
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.85,0:14:23.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種打扮  好難為情
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.25,0:14:26.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係  因為可愛就是正義
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.90,0:14:29.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可真讓人想進行低角度拍攝啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.60,0:14:31.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小岡倫覺得怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.50,0:14:33.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.38,0:14:39.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我  剛才受到了強烈的精神攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.21,0:14:42.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不妙  心…心靈正遭到侵蝕
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.32,0:14:46.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了  凶真師傅
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.03,0:14:48.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又在鬧什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.82,0:14:51.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紅莉栖  嘟嘟嚕
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.17,0:14:58.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,變態助手
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.51,0:15:00.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要盯著全身看來看去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.66,0:15:02.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才沒有呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.19,0:15:04.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又來了  不知廉恥的發展
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.14,0:15:08.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣  這身COS是不是很適合琉佳
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.03,0:15:10.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  非常可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.92,0:15:13.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可愛什麼的  怎麼會…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.67,0:15:15.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別的衣服也穿穿看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.97,0:15:17.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.31,0:15:19.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天來這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.33,0:15:23.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因為有事拜託凶真師傅你們
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.13,0:15:27.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是來穿COS的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.17,0:15:29.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都說了不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.62,0:15:31.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你根本不聽我說話
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.29,0:15:34.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真抱歉  太高興了一不小心就…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.29,0:15:35.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  請求是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.52,0:15:38.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…其實
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.19,0:15:43.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望也能讓我向過去發送簡訊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.17,0:15:44.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.53,0:15:52.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想為沒中六合彩來道歉  然後…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.32,0:15:55.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說  你又發了D-Mail？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.36,0:15:57.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等  怎麼回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.86,0:16:03.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過去改變了  萌郁這個人的存在本身就消失了？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.16,0:16:04.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.69,0:16:06.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.11,0:16:09.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒打算偷聽的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.20,0:16:14.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琉佳  你想往過去發什麼樣的簡訊呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.48,0:16:17.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實際上  我…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.93,0:16:20.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想成為女孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.23,0:16:28.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不太喜歡自己的長相
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.30,0:16:32.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果成為女孩子的話說不定就會多一些自信
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.67,0:16:34.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從以前起就一直這麼想了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.51,0:16:41.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…等一下  她究竟在說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.99,0:16:43.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼哼  助手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.77,0:16:47.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像你犯了一個決定性的錯誤啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.78,0:16:48.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,錯誤？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.22,0:16:52.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琉佳子不是女人  是男的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.18,0:16:54.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.59,0:16:55.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是膚淺
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.75,0:16:57.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也是科學家的話
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.48,0:16:59.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就用自己的眼睛好好看清楚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.47,0:17:07.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼可愛的孩子怎麼可能會是男孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.94,0:17:10.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  稍微…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.10,0:17:18.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.41,0:17:23.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是真心的  真心地想成為女孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.16,0:17:25.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.73,0:17:31.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是就算發了D-Mail  也不知道能不能改變性別
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.57,0:17:33.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有聽說過
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.14,0:17:34.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嬰兒還在肚子裡的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.14,0:17:40.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃很多肉的話就會生男孩  吃很多蔬菜的話就會生女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.62,0:17:46.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說給母親發「要多吃蔬菜哦」的D-Mail？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.93,0:17:48.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  不行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.78,0:17:51.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧  就實現你的願望吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.66,0:17:54.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.14,0:17:56.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了  琉佳
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.28,0:17:56.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.29,0:18:00.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,改變性別什麼的豈不是很不妙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.31,0:18:04.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只不過是吃蔬菜  你覺得會發生這種事情嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.38,0:18:07.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  也不是有科學根據的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.01,0:18:09.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是煩惱很久後才說出來的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.82,0:18:11.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果這樣就能滿足的話
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.60,0:18:13.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琉佳子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.36,0:18:15.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從今天起你就是我們實驗室的一員
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.40,0:18:18.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實驗室成員No.006
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.19,0:18:19.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.41,0:18:21.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼趕緊開始實驗…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.19,0:18:24.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你今年17歲了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.29,0:18:25.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.20,0:18:29.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是1993出生的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.04,0:18:31.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那又怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.81,0:18:35.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手機開始在日本普及是什麼時候
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.47,0:18:42.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是1996年左右
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.19,0:18:45.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,增加簡訊功能的可能會更遲
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.15,0:18:47.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說在漆原出生的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.69,0:18:51.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的母親可能並沒有手機
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.37,0:18:53.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就沒法發送D-Mail嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.88,0:18:54.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.52,0:18:58.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不如改造成可以發送毒電波如何
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.28,0:19:00.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毒電波只要有你們就夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.94,0:19:05.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好棒  再多罵我些吧  可以啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.28,0:19:07.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.18,0:19:12.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是對自己的才能感到害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.30,0:19:13.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你又在說些什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.17,0:19:15.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有手機的話
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.79,0:19:17.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發到呼叫器上不就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.07,0:19:22.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呼叫器  通過電波向小型收信器發送信號的系統
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.96,0:19:26.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在1990年代  爆炸性地普及
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.49,0:19:28.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隨著手機的普及而逐漸沒落
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.36,0:19:30.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呼叫器？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.44,0:19:32.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個還是頭一次見到
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.37,0:19:33.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真熟悉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.59,0:19:35.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是Cel-7而是Cel-circa？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.43,0:19:37.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都寫在那裡  自己看
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.59,0:19:43.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實驗室成員No.006  漆原琉佳
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.63,0:19:44.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是首次任務
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.33,0:19:47.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,調查你母親有沒有呼叫器
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.55,0:19:49.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並得到那號碼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.17,0:19:49.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.60,0:19:55.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽她有呼叫器
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.96,0:19:57.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是號碼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.58,0:20:01.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹得好  你想好簡訊的內容了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.30,0:20:01.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.94,0:20:05.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「吃蔬菜的話就能生出健康的孩子」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.59,0:20:09.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我聽說只能發送18個平假名
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.32,0:20:12.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為呼叫器只能接收數字
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.69,0:20:14.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把這些變換成數字…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.09,0:20:19.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下  濁音點好像要用兩個數字來表示才行
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.39,0:20:23.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能發送的按半形來算最多是36個字元
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.39,0:20:25.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按那種內容的話就超出了4個字元
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.74,0:20:27.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  那麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.01,0:20:30.91,up,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.01,0:20:30.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把這些變換成數字的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.46,0:20:36.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽好了  要啟動了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.41,0:20:36.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.25,0:20:39.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的沒關係嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.48,0:20:40.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.99,0:21:07.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命運探知發動了  也就是說——
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.53,0:21:12.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也有這樣的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.13,0:21:14.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  這個好可愛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.27,0:21:17.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得這個絕對很適合小琉佳啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.53,0:21:19.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.08,0:21:23.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.84,0:21:24.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  變態
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.11,0:21:26.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在盯著哪裡看
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.36,0:21:28.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  不是這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.01,0:21:30.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.29,0:21:34.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「琉佳子成了女孩子了嗎」不太好問
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.15,0:21:35.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.18,0:21:39.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是失敗了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.80,0:21:42.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以說
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.97,0:21:46.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笑嘻嘻地究竟在想像著什麼樣的變態行為
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.85,0:21:47.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  小岡倫
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.16,0:21:52.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  對你們這對變態組合真是容不得半點大意
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.35,0:21:55.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是變態  是變態紳士
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.63,0:21:56.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎樣都無所謂
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.54,0:21:57.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是怎樣都無所謂
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.28,0:22:02.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  世界線確實移動了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.84,0:22:02.43,up,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是阿至不是變態是紳士啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.72,0:22:03.49,up,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你被騙了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.08,0:22:05.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼改變了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.17,0:22:08.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,究竟是什麼


